track.name: Nardis
comments: love the Paris Concert version with the extended intro. get goosebumps when the band jumps in on it

man... simply no words to describe what we've just listened over the last 8 mins...
once again!
great set...really nice eddie gomez solo on bass
Upwards of 20 minutes long when done live with the later trio - see "Last Waltz," for instance.
Not much sound sweeter than a bass standing up.

This track is just amazing.
It got sampled on Unspoken Heard's "Cosmology EP" on the track "Setting Sun", before Madlib used it for "Raid" on the Madvillainy LP -  always loved the sample.
